Syntax
public class ConnectionCallbacksContainer : List<IConnectionCallbacks>, IList<IConnectionCallbacks>, ICollection<IConnectionCallbacks>, IReadOnlyList<IConnectionCallbacks>, IReadOnlyCollection<IConnectionCallbacks>, IEnumerable<IConnectionCallbacks>, IList, ICollection, IEnumerable, IConnectionCallbacks
Remarks

While the interfaces of callbacks wrap up the methods that will be called, the container classes implement a simple way to call a method on all registered objects.
